Tell HN: Profile pages were not loading
text:
Any profile page on HN (URLs of the form https://news.ycombinator.com/user?id={user id}) was not rendering anything apart from the top bar for a few minutes.

I tried different browsers, and devices. The source did not show up when I `curl` it too.

EDIT: They are back up but I'll keep this post up for discussion's sake.
